{"tid":1321152,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【救埋殿後】一齊走？定一齊走唔到","createTime":"2019-07-15T14:57:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T02:09:35.000Z","uid":137789,"like":74,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"0d026ac0c98a83cbdc22616ab1958334aed95527","tid":1321152,"uid":137789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T14:57:44.000Z","msg":"尋晚沙田有一批人俾狗圍到要出龍翔道，其實嗰度睇片都過百人，因為要爬過石墩，做成樽頸位，就係咁，走到最後十幾人時，有狗上前拉住最後一個人，同時間最後一批人唔係過晒就係卡咗喺墩走緊，當中有一個人發現有人被拉住走唔到，即刻好快，比走更快，爬返轉頭救人，片中似乎係兩個都俾狗拉住，其他狗圍埋去，似乎就走唔到，前面百幾人就走得七七八八，條片就完咗<br />\n情況就好似要過河咁，行軍過一啲障礙物就會被切斷，咁殿後嘅都係九死一生，而其實如果過咗河嘅有cover返，殿後嘅係可以唔使死<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n尋片，搵唔返，有人知邊條唔該post上嚟<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外，真係唔該睇兵法戰術典籍，乜都睇下啦，對家真係唔係亂嚟，頂頭操盤係晒計劃，求下大家唔好咁蝕將"},{"pid":"8fe44c2e83fc9a24746e0f18f9b31fbc597817b5","tid":1321152,"uid":137789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T14:59:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c34be770db7cca134b95109e76cb1a0187239c89","tid":1321152,"uid":137789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T14:59:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c2c3d2e28b1848c1d33764b5ce4b8de49e558c4a","tid":1321152,"uid":137789,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T15:14:49.000Z","msg":"要 真 一齊走"},{"pid":"6b824063d0cdfa5bc408546edb93a0e61c596e5a","tid":1321152,"uid":137789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T15:40:57.000Z","msg":"對"},{"pid":"e57de2df1ef56243519596e98ad452609d2391eb","tid":1321152,"uid":137789,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T17:19:35.000Z","msg":"對"},{"pid":"e624fc1c76fe7f7945d08c369ed7823f1027bb60","tid":1321152,"uid":137789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T17:51:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/ah.tortoise/videos/10156189451567204/UzpfSTE0ODI3OTY2NjI6MTAyMjA0MDA0NzAwMzAxNTM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fah.tortoise%2Fvideos%2F10156189451567204%2FUzpfSTE0ODI3OTY2NjI6MTAyMjA0MDA0NzAwMzAxNTM%2F&d=VPbJsUOTS2%2BU35Cb01K8cP2x0mEA6i1FZlyL0j1bjmE%3D&h=b7d26ea6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/ah.tortoise/videos/10156189451567204/UzpfSTE0ODI3OTY2NjI6MTAyMjA0MDA0NzAwMzAxNTM/</a>"},{"pid":"c35393f88daa9050b9850f1e1cfa8b89f621b583","tid":1321152,"uid":137789,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T17:54:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/chan.h.wai.10/videos/10157091339851839/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fchan.h.wai.10%2Fvideos%2F10157091339851839%2F&d=VPbJsUOTS2%2BU35Cb01K8cP2x0mEA6i1FZlyL0j1bjmE%3D&h=f7984b18\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/chan.h.wai.10/videos/10157091339851839/</a><br />\n<br />\n屌，一捉到即刻趕記者，好仆街"},{"pid":"fa38dfcb804960b15cc3c5a0abec008ca528616c","tid":1321152,"uid":249390,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T17:58:53.000Z","msg":"【重組黑警殺人計劃】防暴趕撤退人群出大埔公路比車撞<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1317653\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1317653</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"6e61a277d99e91fb3f6cfc6bdd38259c93f3260e","tid":1321152,"uid":391,"like":26,"dislike":1,"score":25,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T18:18:55.000Z","msg":"其實唔好咁急跳落壆，拉曬手足上黎先一齊走<br />\n你地難爬上壆班狗都難爬，最緊要救曬手足，有人落單比狗捉都可以即刻衝翻去救人<br />\n<br />\n但係現場咁亂好難冷靜咁判斷，所以有經驗嘅巴絲打遇到咁嘅情況記得提下人"},{"pid":"d2383e94f7545ef860a84250a61de85517e0c444","tid":1321152,"uid":149844,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T18:30:39.000Z","msg":"下次你班人可唔可以幫埋殿後先好走<br />\n又少一個力量啦<br />\n個石牆咁高個個自己走完就算"},{"pid":"79e68034d66fc66bdce3cc8e37a1e2ab122256f5","tid":1321152,"uid":258004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T18:30:41.000Z","msg":"有用 幫你推一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7fc23b6c922b39e9557b47f846cd526476b11a7","tid":1321152,"uid":261043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T18:32:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9df8da2fb7573c54473a0241572199aa48cb4845","tid":1321152,"uid":137789,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"6e61a277d99e91fb3f6cfc6bdd38259c93f3260e","tid":1321152,"uid":391,"like":26,"dislike":1,"score":25,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T18:18:55.000Z","msg":"其實唔好咁急跳落壆，拉曬手足上黎先一齊走<br />\n你地難爬上壆班狗都難爬，最緊要救曬手足，有人落單比狗捉都可以即刻衝翻去救人<br />\n<br />\n但係現場咁亂好難冷靜咁判斷，所以有經驗嘅巴絲打遇到咁嘅情況記得提下人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T18:46:04.000Z","msg":"就係質素唔夠囉，一叫啲人睇多啲書諗多啲嘢就起晒槓，想大家好先提點大家，反而俾人屌，不過都唔會放棄，因為真係想幫大家"},{"pid":"1c5de650a360c0974c7fc8805d8864f374b292a3","tid":1321152,"uid":137789,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"d2383e94f7545ef860a84250a61de85517e0c444","tid":1321152,"uid":149844,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T18:30:39.000Z","msg":"下次你班人可唔可以幫埋殿後先好走<br />\n又少一個力量啦<br />\n個石牆咁高個個自己走完就算"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T18:54:26.000Z","msg":"意識好重要，係首要，冇意識先會發生緊或者即將會發生咩事都唔知，真心想幫大家，先至出post<br />\n<br />\n希望勇都唔該睇得自己咁叻，真係仲有好多進步空間，好多時啲人以為自己勇係帶領著成個運動，唔肯聽人講，講多兩句就話各有各做，咩嘢現場決定，完咗都唔准檢討，其實唔聽人講，拒絕進步，最終必然會拖到運動嘅後腳"},{"pid":"63e98335ca25cab49ff5f61a42440e95d60b244b","tid":1321152,"uid":63117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T18:54:52.000Z","msg":"黑警死全家"},{"pid":"d3b186c3b53ba5c06d1212f67c03dead81ff5ddc","tid":1321152,"uid":36411,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T19:00:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a214637288cdde9e428fc8fbc72b465b7997b9ad","tid":1321152,"uid":174120,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T19:00:43.000Z","msg":"大家吸經  總之記住  顧住後面手足"},{"pid":"7fee9035ace8fe62d08969fbee9e59ed99ca1dda","tid":1321152,"uid":50347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T19:06:57.000Z","msg":"對唔住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5f909b05737fb377a73fc666c7b875b6c6129c9","tid":1321152,"uid":137789,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d3b186c3b53ba5c06d1212f67c03dead81ff5ddc","tid":1321152,"uid":36411,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T19:00:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T19:20:39.000Z","msg":"意識比一切都重要<br />\n<br />\n行軍中留意隊形，唔好斷，斷開好易出事，可能俾狗中間截擊<br />\n<br />\n尾隊留意最後殿後嘅，任何時候，有事要嗌出嚟，隊尾可以變返隊頭，最緊要係俾人知，求援<br />\n<br />\n因為冇大台，冇人物，有嘅只係我哋每一個人，所以唔會太有指揮，只可以靠大家嘅意識，而呢啲意識係要培養嘅，多啲同身邊嘅人傾，交換知識，增進見聞<br />\n<br />\n點解會有口號口訣，因為可以統一傳播意識，易記，大家諗到口訣可以分享下<br />\n<br />\n點解好多時對手唔難應付？因為佢哋係受過訓練，又行動一致，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">對方每次出事都係有啲白痴行動唔一致引起，我方何嘗唔係呢？</span></span>淨係升級裝備根本唔會夠，一定要普及化一啲重要嘅意識"},{"pid":"8ec0c6a3b4756eb294bceb19724a7b7f6db0198a","tid":1321152,"uid":46241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T23:13:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fb55da9c8bd8cc01e91b1a521eb4258a03715eaa","tid":1321152,"uid":152584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d3b186c3b53ba5c06d1212f67c03dead81ff5ddc","tid":1321152,"uid":36411,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T19:00:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T23:30:13.000Z","msg":"夢境入面，佢有個綠衫無啦啦行出嚟 跟住同佢地講走緊啦  同時叫人上馬路 當時好多人無心理準備衝出馬路  綠衫有6個左右 有個即出椒 前面又被圍堵 頂唔住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbc57f1bb11695761646243690932ef39bbe3d1f","tid":1321152,"uid":152584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fb55da9c8bd8cc01e91b1a521eb4258a03715eaa","tid":1321152,"uid":152584,"like":